tags.description: Walk through a forty-acre forest and smell the wildflowers. Take a stroll by Greenwood Creek and listen to the birds sing. With the exception of the scenic hiking trails, this area remains virtually untouched to maintain a natural, aesthetic environment
tags.name: Greenwood Park
